@node requirements
@title "Requirements"

 This transfer animation requires Voyager (NG), although it is also usable  with
 IBrowse or AWeb (II) ... but that would not make any sense in my opinion.

 A graphic board is recommended, but not required, because of the five different
 colour depths (24 down to 4 Bit).

 BTW: The difference between the 24 and 8 Bit version is hardly to be seen.

@endnode

@node install
@title "How to install??"

 If you are a very,  very  experienced  user,  you  can  install  this  transfer
 animation "by hand" 8-). Otherwise wait for an installer script.

 No  ...  still kidding. There is and there will be no installer script for this
 transfer animation.

 To install just grab the prefered colour depth/style (including icon) and  copy
 those files as 'TransferAnim(.info)' to the root directory of your Voyager (NG)
 location(... don't  forget  to  backup  the  original  transfer  animation  ...
 although there's no need anymore ;-)).

 It should not be that hard to install ...
 
@endnode

